#: ../../ip-config/network-objects.rst:73
msgid "DNS forward lookup zone"
msgstr "Forward Lookup Zone für DNS-Einträge"

#: ../../ip-config/network-objects.rst:74
msgid ""
"The forward lookup zone where hosts from the network should be added must"
